	<hr>
	<font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">Please be advised that lurking among these forums are the filthiest, most vile and pugnant creatures to ever make their way to the Berthall. Once cast away by the powers that be, these beings have been granted passage to portions of the site which even moderators and admins fear to tread.
<br>

<br>
These Board Trolls roam this forum so becarefull and enter at your own risk, for the protection of the admin/moderators won't follow you here.
<br>

<br>
We must uphold our privacy policy even in this forum in addition, here are some provisions not yet mentioned in the <a href="/privacy.php">Privacy Policy.</a>
<br>

<br>
1) We will remove/edit any material which escapes the realm of fantasy roleplaying which is the reason we are all gathered here. Personal information about any board member falls under this provision.
<br>

<br>
2) We do not claim to be associated with any particular game, any information which is asked to be removed by offical representatives of the games discussed on these forums will be honored at our discretion.
<br>

<br>
3) We will never give any information to any 3rd party organization or other message board members about our members without prior consent by those involved. All registration information is considered private.
<br>

<br>

<br>

<br>
Take it easy and enjoy the mayhem.
<br>

<br>
-The Berthall Staff.</font>
